CommitDate: Mon Jun 22 16:05:58 2026 +0800

    fix(pinmux): restore I2C3/I2C9/CAN2/CAN3 pins reset to rsvd on JP7.2
    
    JP7.2 pinmux (xlsm Rev.9->Rev.14) reset these pins to rsvd1 while the
    controllers stay enabled in DT, causing bus timeouts (e.g. i2cset bus 3
    "Write failed"). Restore to JP7.1 functions in the MB1 BCT pinmux.

